ml shot = $2.50</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"image2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0407/5103/8632/files/DSCF7295-2_dd914881-9a98-4334-ba68-3a5866bd590a.jpg?v=1663533058\" style=\"width:100%\"></div>\n</div>",
